Enclosing class:
Console
public class Console.ObjectIterator<T extends sailpoint.object.SailPointObject>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Console.ClosableDecachableIterator<T>

ObjectIterator allows for SailPointObjects to be iterated over without creating Hibernate cache and memory scaling issues the context.getObjetcs and context.search(class, QueryOptions) method presents. This iterator can be safely closed with any resource leaks.

Author:
christian.cairney
